Wow, I'm in Missouri now. 

Ben's back in Houston, which sucks, but oh well. You win and lose.

I work at Wal Mart now, so it's uber-spiff. 6.30/hr isn't though. but at least I'm fulltime. 

I'm getting my own place soon as well as getting roommates, so that's cool.

I'm living with my mother though, which isn't.

I can't wait for Ben to get back, we'll finally be together again, and I'll be happy. ^^;; 


Oh, my mom's putting me in counsiling because I'm "Depressed". She kicked Ben out, so that's where the depression came from. But..Yeah.

Other than that, I'm pretty bored. 

Anyone got a Martini?



xoxoxox


<3 ben

Well... Sad news. 

One of my best friends, Zach is dead.

._. 

He was driving somewhere in Oklahoma, and got into an accident.. Then he was thrown from the windsheild and died like.. 3 hours later. I didn't even know until he had been dead for like.. 10 hours. :\ 



It makes me so fucking depressed.. And Ben's never been around me this depressed before.. So I don't think he knows how to handle it really. I think I'm just sounding like a bitch to him.. Although he's trying his best (in his own way) to be supportive. 

I dunno.. With Zachs death, and me thinking, it hasn't been a great impact on my school work. 


The limit for tardies is 7 and absences is 4. 


I have 23 absences in my first period class. I have still yet to be called in.


I think they really want me to graduate this year, so they're overlooking it or something. 






MAN!


Something smells like SHIT in here!




Ew. I figured it out. There's shoes with dogshit on them nearby. 


But anyways.. Yeah. So I've been depressed and bitchy. Kinda a 180 from how I've been feeling before this weekend... God I just want to slice my fucking arms open and snort myself retarded.



I just wish that one day... Just ONE day... Me and Ben could sit at 'home' and do nothing but hang out together.. WITHOUT whining about doing something. ._. 





-Sighs- 





I need to adjust my life again. 




I love you, Ben.



.x.x.x.

Sooo... 

It's been a while. 


But I'm back.

I have a computer now too. >:D


Nothing too awesome has happened lately. I turned 19, I graduate Dec. 16th... Ben just turned 23.. Uhm.. I don't talk to that stinky fucking loser Charlie anymore. His bitch ass can rot in that rat-infested, torn down, rotting, stinking, shithole of a Winnebago for all I fucking care. And Jason can rot in hell along with him. That bitch ass motherfucker stole $400 worth of stuff from me and Ben...An x-box, and two guns... I think one was a .38, and the other was one of those ones which look like a police gun. THEN he had the nerve to try and say that he "lost" everything. BS. I'll beat that fat-fucks ass. Then JoBeth.. Hah. That little slut is gone again, and for all everyone cares she can stay gone. As Erich says, "I'll slice her fuckin' throat if I see her again."...But whatever. 

So.. I had Thanksgiving in Kemah. That was awesome, actually. They had this little dog there, and it had one red and one blue eye, and it was awesome. ..o.O;; But my grandmothers dog was about to become a football.. >:/ That stupid fuckin' mutt. I HATE that dog. 

Oh yeah. I live in one of those Car-tents now.. xD Lmfao. I'm such a bum for no reason. I'll be getting a place soon though. I need to anyways. Me and Ben can't keep mooching off my grandmother for a place to live. ... In fact she said that we have to be out by Christmas. ....So.. Whatever. 


Basically, those are the MAJOR things happening. Oh.. And Jackson, Andrew, Charlie, Chris, Ryan, and that other dude who I don't know the name of are going to die. >:/ No one fucking bitch-jumps me and Ben. NO ONE. And a ONE-ON-ONE fight is between TWO people, not Seven. 

Yeah.. Whatever basically.

.x.x.x.

Ben's Baaackk.. 

So me = Feeling loads better lately. 


Anywho. Not much to write about. I got a 30 pack of beer for mine an' Ben's 6 month Anniversary and the dude we were sharing it with stole it. I found that fucked--but I still have his sword. :X Hmm.. Sell the sword and get $100-500... Or give it back and forgive him for stealing 15 cheap beers?  ... >:/ And fucking over some of my friends... AND taking advantage of my bad ass "Can you bum a dollar?" awesomeness. Bascically, He'd make me go to EVERY gas station on Fairbanks N Houston (Well, not all, only about 10 of 'em) and spange at LEAST $2 for gas. I find that fucked seeing as I only asked him for a ride that takes 5 minutes to drive, 10 minutes in absolute traffic.  Anywho.. Going on. Today's gonna be a good day. I'll see Ben soon enough.. And I'm gonna get those mad-crazy-awesome eggrolls on Antione. 



btw: I got ym mad ben sex. :XXXXXXXXXXXX .... >>;; Yehp. 

i<3 ben still.

=\ I miss ben. A lot. I finally got a letter from him, and of course, it made me REALLY happy. ^^; ... ._. It was so cute, and loving, and emotional all at once that I nearly cried... I only sucked it up because I knew I had to walk out of my room soon to go get a pepsi, and I didn't want Machell seeing me cry. The only time she ever has seen me cry was when I came back the night he got locked up... And I couldn't even ask her for the ride I needed, JoBeth had to. JoBeth is really on my top Best buddie list right now for everyone who reads this' information. She's helped me out so much it isn't even funny... ;.; <3 Jo. But anywho.. I don't like people seeing me cry, obviously, so when I walked in (half drunk due to a few beers recently chugged.. >>; ) I ran straight to my room, and JoBeth asked her for me. I couldn't even talk.. It was even harder to tell his mother though.. :\ She has soooo many pictures of him hanging up.. I was just looking around the whole time trying not to cry.. But I did anyways.. =\ I'm such a pansy. Bleh. Anywho... ><; Things are working out for the better.. ^^; I get to visit him soon!!! Which each visit means a step closer to Rehab sex ;x ...Which is all I'm getting for the next two years.. e.e; But oh well. @_@; I'm in love. I can't help this shit! So anywhoooooo... >>; ... Oh yeah! I went to the gay pride parade last weekend. That ws fun minus having to haul Laurens shit around in my bag.. >:\ I wanted to/still want to kill her because of that damned night. She was fucking spun the whole time we were at the O (gay club) and I was sober.. and FUCK. Being sober around tweakers SUCKS! ><;; They get all bitchy.. And annoying.. And I want to rip their heads off. o.o;; ... Oh yeah! but anywho.. I took 10 bazillion pictures.. >>; Well, really more like 60.. And I'll post some soon. >:D I got me a computer. WHOOOOOOO!!!!!!!!! >:DDD!! ... e.e; Well, Almost. I have to get the monitor hook up working properly.. THEN I have a computer.. ^^; Which = major onlinage. Also major d/l'ness. @_@; Mmmm... ATHF Tattoo's. ... xD I am os getting Frylock, Master SHake, and Meatwad tattoo'd on my body somewhere. I will DEFENATELY post those pictures.. o_o; Sorry.. I'm spazzing.. xD Me Nikki and JoBeth all had an eating contest at Pancho's (Mexican buffet place) for JoBeths birthday.. xD We all lost.. And couldn't move for like.. 10 mins due to over eating.. Omfg.. That was like.. 10 hours ago and I'm still overly full. i love pancho's. xD ...Ehm. Anyways.. o.O; Yeah. I double lied. I thought this was gonna be a short post, but it's actually a long one.. >>; Reason for the title up there btw.. >>;; So.. Yeh. o.o; Time for sleep. >:O ROB! YOU ARE SUCH A WHORE! You said you were gonna be online.. ;.; YOU'RE THE LIAR!! >:O -Jumpscreampunkmoshsing- YOU'RE A LI-LI-LI-LI-LIE! YOU'RE A LI-LI-LI-LI-LIE! xD Omfg. Sid is hot. ;.; I still love Ben though. He's my forever hot'ness. Key part of his letter, "I cna't wait until I'm out of here. We're going to have a lot of catching up to do." XDDDD OMFGrgekljhgatoi ;.; I need Ben's sex. >:O Fuck songs that remind me of him. Ehm.. Yes. Mucho rambling.. >>;; I'll stfu. btw... I think I'm the only one I know allergic to meth. hawp. i <3 ben. ;.;

Hm.. 

I was just reading some of my old LJ's ( mistress_courti, razorskiss, publicityscam, ruby_goddess, etc.. ) when I realized something. 

I used to be utterly obsessed with Rob. 


o.O; Which I see as kind of odd now, because I still call him and shit, but it's only like.. " Hey, how's it goin' man?"  and BS like that. 


ANYWAYS... >>; 



:\ I really miss Ben. It's been Over a month since I've last heard anything from him. I don't know whether to be worried, or to stay calm, or to just sit back and wait impatiently.. =\ I love that fucker. ._. Y'know.. the 18th will be our 5 month anniversary. =\ I hope he calls me before then.. Or at least writes me. Dear fucking spirits I miss him.. ;.;...



I drew some drawings last night.. Just doodles really.. A Frankenstien doing the Monster Mash, a Butterfly screaming ( Listen to "scream of the Butterfly" by Acid Bath, you'd understand. ), a Chef saying, "Nice cookin' Tex!" and then on the opposite page, a picture of a cowboy with a nametag that says "TEX" ... ANd he's screaming, " Thank ya' partner! GUH-QUAH!" 



Meh.. I need a cig and some sleep. Yeah.. 9 am and I still haven't gone to bed. JoBeth will be up within the hour too.. e.e;; Fuck. 


=\ I'll post more next time. Promise. 



>>; LEave me some lovin's.

If i was a serial killer i would be Charles Manson.

Charles Manson... the only serial killer that faces life in prison, yet never actually killed anyone.

Manson believed that by starting a cult, and manipulating his followers with drugs and mental suggestion he would get them to think he was the next messiah, and force them into doing anything he said, he was right.

One night in the Hollywood hills, Manson set out his minions to attack the home of the head of a record label that rejected his work years back. That night they murdered 5 people one of which was Sharon Tate who was also eight months pregnant at the time. Shooting and stabbing their victims repeatedly and smearing the words "Die Pig Die", and "Helter Skelter" over the walls.

Manson thought that by doing these killings that it would start a race war between blacks and whites. He also believed that the Beatles wrote many of their songs for and about him.

First of all, I want to state that I HAD my lip peirced. I had to remove it because it got infected.. >>;; But oh well. ... Which leads to something else--I got kicked out of school. o_O; For the lip peircing might I add.

Ehm... Lets see...

Oh! I made a promise to Ben. ^^; I'm staying drug free as long as he is behaving. ... So far I've pretty much kept it...>>; minus the crystal episode, but he got into a fight right before they shipped him off to Cenkor, so it evens out.

I miss Mike. ._.

It's been over 2 yrs since he's died, but for some reason I just don't think he's dead. I denno, mebbe I'm just going crazy... But I just miss him. It's safe to say that I loved him, and that I still do love him. :\ There's not a day that goes by that I don't think of him.. And I used to have his picture in my wallet which I carried around everywhere, but then it got stolen. ><; So.. No more picture of Mike. :\

I don't know if it's from lack of sleep, or from just being plain annoyed today... but I just feel like tearing everything to shreds. And I don't think I'd feel one bit guilty about doing so either. :\ 


Bleh. I feel like ass. I'm gonna try to get some sleep. I haven't had any in about two days.


Wish me luck people.

well, tonight was exciting. I got drunk and tried to burn cd's and talk to people which in the end made me tired so i went to my room and passed out. It was funnier whenever I was trying to take a shower. I would lay down in the bathtub with the shower running.. then I'd turn on the bath part when I stood up.. xD lmfao. I get so retarded when drunk. Oh yeah. Gary = Awesome. I think I might go out with him on Friday. GREAT NEWS! Me and JoBeth and Erich and Aaron are all getting a place in tomball! :D AKA: I'm gonna be moving out and getting to be able to do tons and tons of fun stuff. >>; + i'm getting a computer and roadrunner ( LMao it always makes me think of "Johnny be good" by the sex pistols.. Lmfao.. ) such goodness. Oh. And I haven't talked to my dad yet about it.. Soooooo... >>;.... .... .......... Yeah. I don't know what I'm going to say. But I think he knows. e.e;; Err.. This is such a responcibility. o.o; Boo! Oh.. My friend said that whenever he did meth that he got REALLY artistic.. AKA: He was drawing a lot. Sooo.. I'm thinking that when they get meth this weekend I was gonna do some after I took my sketch book over there. o.O; Hm.. I believe I'm destroying my body with drugs ciggarettes and alcohol. ...Woo. well, I'm not a big druggie. Wait wait.. Here's a list of drugs I've taken: Weed (hardly a drug/hardly smoked) cocaine weed+cocaine(only once. ><; It's sooo nasty.) shrooms bars bars + alcohol shrooms + driving while a bad trip ( This is REALLY scary. o_o; I'll tell that story soon ) And repeat mixed more and more. See? Not a big druggie at all. but I wouldn't mind adding meth, x, and acid. Ok, the shroom story. so me and Tim go get some shrooms( 175 g in about an hour ).. Make tea.. Drink the tea with erich jobeth charlie and a tiny bit with josh. I need to remind everyone out there that that was my first time trippin'.. o.o; So.. everythings goin' good. People are laughing.. I'm seeing a graveyard outside erichs door... Tim and Erich are talking.. ..-.-;; Bad thing. Tim = Easily freaked. Erich = Doesn't want the government finding him. So Aaron is in the back getting ready to spark up a joint and all the sudden Erich screams " If you light that we're all going to die!" Tim flips. ( I might add that I was having a good trip untill this happens ) He runs outside and starts screaming for me etc etc.. Then finally charlie says " Hey, tim is caling you" .. and I'm all.. " O_O... Oh.. ? -Walks outside to Tim-" So yeah.. He grabs me by the arm and starts rambling on about how we're not safe how he loves me too much that he doesn't want to see me dead etc etc etc.. And we get into his car. (I would like to mention that this is only about 30 mins into the trip. e.e; So we still had a way to go.) So he drives off, making me leave my jacket ( while it's cold) my keys and a few other things.. PLUS.. I didn't say goodbye to my friends so they didnt know what the fuck happened to me. So we're driving back to his house.. The WHOLE way there I kept seeing cars smash into the front end of his car. So I'm doing the bad trippin'. So is he. He wasn't as bad though, he was only thinking we were GOING to die.. I kept thinking that we WERE dying. So... We get back to his place. He makes me lay down with him and go to bed right away. Do I sleep? No. The next few hours I'm just staring at the hideous faces glareing and snapping at me that were coming out of the celing and walls, along with knocking off all of the bugs that were crawling all over me. e.e;; Then the shrooms wore off and I laughed at him. o.O; Pretty fucked, huh? Wow, this is the longest post in a long while. o.o; Woo me. -thumbs up yay!-

Well, if you couldn't tell, that was my fucked up way of wrapping things up, because I just got a phone call from my uncle. School, here I come. Fuck you. -Ti

Well, Iknow it's been forever since an update, and there are reasons, but I just can't seem to get them out of my mouth at the moment. I read something earlyer, and I'll post it in a cut-tag for those people who don't want to read it.. But.. here it is. 

<lj-cut text="L0ckes view">its 4:11AM.
they all went to bed.
ive been thinking of things all day.. 
i didnt want to bother you too much earlier. i know you were busy.
so i wrote this so that you could read it later when you had time


do we need a cure?
maybe we can just quit.. just forget what you do. forget the people you 
know. not suicide.. just walking away from your whole life. NOW.

why not? because they love you? because you love them? because
youre afraid to be alone? because you wont get the money and 
the car and the girl/guy and the house? the fufillment of following 
through a lifes worth of hard work doing the single job youve 
chosen to specialize at? why cant we just get up and disappear 
one day?  


what do you do when everything that you know means nothing?


keep trying to grab onto this one reason to live.
keep trying to understand a dream i know has no meaning
putting together random facts, words and statements looking
for some universal pattern. some concept that everyone else 
was born with but i have to learn.. somehow.. the hard way.
if i cry during a movie at the part where the director wanted
me to cry.. then are those tears even real? all the hundreds of
people who worked on that film knew i was supposed to cry at
that moment, so how can that be authentic? 
so do i stare at the truth and burn in its honesty
or do i just find happiness in a blind lie?

i keep hoping i'll wake up one day and i'll suddenly know
some cosmic truth. like a scalding shower suddenly switched cold.
i keep hoping that something will happen that will let me know 
the next piece of the puzzle. maybe someone in my family will
die and then i'll know what to do next. it'll be all cleared up
once my tears dry and im on my way home from the movie 
i'll know the whole plot then, and i'll know what comes next.
what if there is no truth? nothing to believe in?
what if we are all just here? and when you die thats it.
will it really matter what you did when you were here?
does it matter if you did well? if people hated you or liked you?
or if if you were happy or sad? 


if two people are in a room. just sitting there.
why do they have to react to eachother?
why do we talk to eachother?
kill eachother
love eachother?
we used to pray that we would be hit by a car.
injured.. deformed.. disabled somehow so that we could say 
LOOK! SEE? THIS IS WHY I AM THIS WAY! THIS IS MY EXSCUSE!
i dont care.. i cant make myself care.. i cant get out of this
bed and shut the door.. so i'll sit here and listen to you screaming
at me. sweating under this blanket til i rot right through the frame 
and into the floor. its summer and lovers are with one another, 
smiling and laughing, content with one another so nothing else matters.
expression? communication? survival instinct?
who cares. he says. i love you. she says. sigh. they say.


i'll try to call you tomorrow..

-L0cke
</lj-cut>
